# Repo Defaults

{{#IF_MONOREPO}}
- This repo is a `{{PACKAGE_MANAGER}}` workspace monorepo.
- Unless explicitly requested, work in `{{PRIMARY_APP_DIR}}` rather than other apps.
{{/IF_MONOREPO}}
- Prefer project-specific facts from the repo over generic framework advice.
- Do not create or update docs unless the user asked for docs or the task explicitly includes documentation work.
- Exception: allow docs/rules/skills updates when the task explicitly requires contract alignment or knowledge-sync remediation.
- Do not start local dev servers automatically for verification; the user starts them when needed.
- Keep rules short, current, and scoped.
